<p class="">That does not appear to be a question which could properly be put to me or which I should answer. This House decided to establish this form of procedure, and I apprehend that it would not be for this House to ask for the assent of the Director of Public Prosecutions in such a matter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
